      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     move  all "."        to   rf-dcc-rag-soc         .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-dcc-rag-soc       to   w-det-rag-int-rag      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-rag-900.
       prn-liv-det-rag-300.
